                "points": [
                  "Higher priority job execution",
                  "Efficient use of resources"
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "key_facts": [
          "An operating system is a piece of software that manages computer hardware and software resources.",
          "The primary goal of an operating system is to provide a platform for application software."
        ],
        "exam_corner": [
          "Understand the definition and purpose of an operating system.",
          "Be able to identify the different types of operating systems."
